  sentances:
  - To the left of the health circle you can see 3 icons
  - Those icons represent the 3 different attacks you can have active at one time
  - 'Each attack is mapped to buttons: 1, 2 and 3. You can change the current attack
    by pressing the appropiate key'
  - You can execute an attack by pressing left click. Each time you attack a significant
    portion of your energy meter is depleted
  - Your character does not attack directly. Each attack action spawns an shadow of
    your character.
  - Each shadow has a delay before attacking and has a different attack. Exercise
    caution vefore deciding to engage the enemy
